The purpose of this study is to estimate antihypertensive effect of azilsartan medoxomil (Edarbi(R)) therapy on blood pressure in participants with overweight or obesity in routine clinical practice of hypertension (HTN) treatment in the Russian Federation and in the Republic of Kazakhstan.

